  "detailed_description": "<h1>Add to wishlist!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/d3116958142692ec9a3d10a9bcd534dc.poster.avif?t=1752838123\" width=560 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/d3116958142692ec9a3d10a9bcd534dc.webm?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/d3116958142692ec9a3d10a9bcd534dc.mp4?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/404322343cf4dcfb59204ec11fd9a5cd.poster.avif?t=1752838123\" width=444 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/404322343cf4dcfb59204ec11fd9a5cd.webm?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/404322343cf4dcfb59204ec11fd9a5cd.mp4?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>UNHOLY VILLAGE</strong> is a single-player thriller and survival game. The village you visit for your sister's funeral has actually been taken over by a demon, and you must try to break its curse.<br>Once a peaceful village, it faced a mysterious curse. The village began to live in fear because of the infected entities that suddenly appeared. Over time, the village became an uninhabitable and cursed place.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Try to save your friends</h2>After the car accident, you must search for your friends' traces in the abandoned village and find them before they die.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/1a2bf6e4bbed0fcef7c77e9c50426b57.poster.avif?t=1752838123\" width=444 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/1a2bf6e4bbed0fcef7c77e9c50426b57.webm?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/1a2bf6e4bbed0fcef7c77e9c50426b57.mp4?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Realistic graphics, immersive cinematics, and rich story</h2>Unholy Village; with realistic graphics, cinematics, and rich storytelling, will enhance your gameplay experience and bring you tension, fear, and excitement.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/8162f0403cd8d57bf05e1751c3ba126c.poster.avif?t=1752838123\" width=444 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/8162f0403cd8d57bf05e1751c3ba126c.webm?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/8162f0403cd8d57bf05e1751c3ba126c.mp4?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Try to survive</h2>Hide, seek refuge, and most importantly, survive from infected creatures, the demon, and psychotic humans in an abandoned and cursed village!<br>Collect weapon ammunition, bandages, and medical supplies from abandoned houses in the village.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warning</h2>Contains blood, weapons, and frightening graphics.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/404322343cf4dcfb59204ec11fd9a5cd.poster.avif?t=1752838123\" width=444 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/404322343cf4dcfb59204ec11fd9a5cd.webm?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/404322343cf4dcfb59204ec11fd9a5cd.mp4?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>UNHOLY VILLAGE</strong> is a single-player thriller and survival game. The village you visit for your sister's funeral has actually been taken over by a demon, and you must try to break its curse.<br>Once a peaceful village, it faced a mysterious curse. The village began to live in fear because of the infected entities that suddenly appeared. Over time, the village became an uninhabitable and cursed place.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Try to save your friends</h2>After the car accident, you must search for your friends' traces in the abandoned village and find them before they die.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/1a2bf6e4bbed0fcef7c77e9c50426b57.poster.avif?t=1752838123\" width=444 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/1a2bf6e4bbed0fcef7c77e9c50426b57.webm?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/1a2bf6e4bbed0fcef7c77e9c50426b57.mp4?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Realistic graphics, immersive cinematics, and rich story</h2>Unholy Village; with realistic graphics, cinematics, and rich storytelling, will enhance your gameplay experience and bring you tension, fear, and excitement.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/8162f0403cd8d57bf05e1751c3ba126c.poster.avif?t=1752838123\" width=444 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/8162f0403cd8d57bf05e1751c3ba126c.webm?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780610/extras/8162f0403cd8d57bf05e1751c3ba126c.mp4?t=1752838123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Try to survive</h2>Hide, seek refuge, and most importantly, survive from infected creatures, the demon, and psychotic humans in an abandoned and cursed village!<br>Collect weapon ammunition, bandages, and medical supplies from abandoned houses in the village.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warning</h2>Contains blood, weapons, and frightening graphics.",
